quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  18,84,"Minen, Min weeɓinanno mo ka leydi, Min ngokki mo immorde e kala hu'unde sabu."
  18,85,"O jokki sabu[laawol}"
  18,86,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka mutirde na'ange ngen o tawi henge muta e loope ɓaleeje, o tawi ton yimɓe : Min mbi'i'i: "Ko aan yo jom galaaɗi ɗiɗi, ko si a leptay ma si a jogitoto e maɓɓe ko moƴƴi."
  18,87,"O wi'i: Si tawii ko on tooñuɗo min lepta mo, refti o ruttee ka Joomi makko o lepta mo lepte añiiɗe"."
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gooŋɗinɗo o golli ko moƴƴi no woodani mo njoɓdi moƴƴiri ndin, aray min n mbi'ana mo e fiyaake amen on neweende."
  18,89,"Refti o jokki laawol."
  18,90,"Haa de o yottinoo ka ƴellitorde na'ange nge, o tawi henge ƴellitoo e dow yimɓe, Min mbaɗanaani ɓe ga magge heeɗo."
  18,91,"Ko wano nii, gooɗii Min kuɓindike ko woni kon ka makko e ganndal."
  18,92,"Refti o jokki laawol."
  18,93,"Haa nde o yottinoo hakkunde heedooji ɗi ɗiɗio tawi ga majji yimɓe ɓe ɗeɓataa faamde konngol."
  18,94,"Ɓe mbi'i: eey ma Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ko bonnooɓe ka leydi. Enee, min waɗante njeenaari fii yo a waɗ hakkunde amen e maɓɓe heedo?"
  18,95,"O wi'i: "Ko Joomi am weeɓinani kan kon ɓuri moƴƴude, walliree kan doole mi waɗa hakkunde mo'on e maɓɓe heedo"."
  18,96,"Ngaddanee kam kunte njamɗe haa nde o feppi- ndirnoo hakkunde naɗe ɗen ɗiɗi, o wi'i: "pifee haa nde o waɗnoo ɗum yiite, o wi'i: ngaddanee kam sila mi wancina e dow mum"."
  18,97,"Ɓe kattantaa ƴellitagol ndi, ɓe hattantaa kadi julgol ndi."